urlText: City Circle: Trains will not run on the City Circle
content:
Friday 8 September
  • From 11pm to 1.30am, trains will not run on the City Circle.
  • T1 North Shore & Western and T9 Northern Line trains continue to run, stopping at Central, Town Hall and Wynyard.
  • T4 Eastern Suburbs Line trains continue to run between Central and Bondi Junction, stopping at Town Hall, Martin Place and Kings Cross.
  • For travel to other City stations use the light rail or local bus services.

  • Trackwork also affects trains on other lines.

  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date real time information. You can also subscribe to planned trackwork alerts.
subtitle: City Circle: Trains will not run on the City Circle

urlText: Train trackwork on the City Circle and T1 North Shore Line may affect how you travel
content:
Saturday 9 and Sunday 10 September   
  • Train trackwork on the City Circle and T1 North Shore Line may affect how you travel.
  • Trains will not run on the City Circle, or between Central and Wynyard. For travel around the City use the light rail between Central and Circular Quay or local bus services.
  • If you are travelling to T1 North Shore Line stations change at Wynyard, not Central, to continue your journey.

urlText: Buses replace trains between Port Kembla and Wollongong, and between Dapto and Waterfall
content:
Saturday 16 September
  • From 3am to 11am, buses replace trains between Port Kembla and Wollongong, and between Dapto and Waterfall.
  • Trains run between Bomaderry, Kiama and Dapto, some to a changed timetable.

  • Replacement buses may be impacted by driver shortages. We are doing all we can to minimise the impact to your journey and provide a safe service, however cancellations or delays may occur.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date real time information. You can also subscribe to planned trackwork alerts.
Bus routes
11SC Dapto, Wollongong, North Wollongong then Waterfall and return
14SC Dapto, then all stations to Thirroul and return
27SC Port Kembla, then all stations to Wollongong and return
48SC Otford, Helensburgh Town Centre, then Helensburgh Station and return
52SC Thirroul, all stations to Waterfall via Helensburgh Town and return (bypassing Otford and Helensburgh Station)
54SC Thirroul, then express to Waterfall and return
